******************
*    RGBlocks    *
******************
Version: 2.0

RGBlocks is an advanced tetris-like game with a lot of special effects (rotating scene, shooting, etc),
explosions, console, sfx and music. Play to see the rest of the features.
Libraries:
- SDL
- SDL_mixer
- GL, GLU

To compile RGBlocks, run:
        make
Then as root enter:
        make install
to properly install all game files.

After that you can start the game by entering:
        RGBlocks
